<p>In the latest development, French authorities arrested two people in connection with last week&#x27;s theft of imperial-era crown jewels from the Louvre Museum in Paris, including one man detained as he tried to leave France from Charles de Gaulle airport . Investigators said video surveillance and DNA traces left at the scene helped identify the suspects, and prosecutors warned that public disclosure of the arrests could hamper the hunt for the missing jewels . The stolen collection is valued at about $100–$102 million, and investigators have mobilised a large team to recover the items and trace accomplices .</p><img src='https://kagiproxy.com/img/CLHvac3xaNnSupOh8lgUFPTUbDYY4QSegajC3v7qqSBC4_U4JE9qXa2PLzghepQE2SJ6wNJ3ka2HkprOw8lTFetuAZ5FPCOTF79hdN69kWdPPKo9j7H1TTHUDpOuwS0A2FUHU3vHY-OPDk7Qs9T4M5WWKDMpi_WjmZtbqGMxCtzSBU5PXsrfAlqGH_tmQFeAba7-1bBcHfFF-BsXgo-u2JkE5WNAo0KdEilcbuEpkZT3ykeQJZHBYoytVtWHadNBs9gP846hw5Nrp7x1U7TYD7Pxp3Hm7QN6oFq09yamvn_ZbqautJ1LV3baygcCxGfcpKQdWKuSQwNs83IR-p17k7bVNg9kZPFrS2Mq6txH-lSvkBe92Rng-4f3GQaO2bfcbePB5N99dyGjZQa_XxOG5fNdUZriWJg7zAM6RdW5by-wtwf1xZsD895CQbw8TN8xenBAq8f6x24SjLse6Beh2CEOZr1r_1gqVVJM' alt='Police and investigators outside the Louvre following the crown jewels theft' /><br /><h3>Highlights:</h3><ul><li>Method of entry: Authorities say the burglars used a stolen movers&#x27; truck and an extendable basket lift or crane to reach a first-floor gallery before cutting through a window, executing the raid in under seven minutes</li><li>Forensic haul: Investigators collected more than 150 DNA samples from helmets, gloves and tools left at the scene, giving teams multiple leads to match to suspects</li><li>Inside-job probe: Prosecutors and press reports say digital forensics have prompted detectives to examine possible collusion by a museum security employee as part of the inquiry</li><li>Museum safeguards: After the robbery the Louvre moved some of its most valuable jewels to the Bank of France and faces scrutiny over a camera that was reportedly pointing away from the break-in site</li></ul><blockquote>Carried out arrests on Saturday evening - Laure Beccuau</blockquote><h3>Perspectives:</h3><ul><li>Paris prosecutor&#x27;s office (Laure Beccuau): Officials announced arrests and asked for discretion, warning that public revelations could hinder efforts by the roughly 100 investigators on the case. (<a href='https://www.dawn.com/news/1951498/2-suspects-held-for-louvre-jewel-heist'>Dawn</a>)</li><li>Louvre director (Laurence des Cars): The museum director told lawmakers a nearby camera was &#x27;pointing in the wrong direction&#x27; and described the theft as a serious failure that has prompted security reviews. (<a href='https://www.rt.com/news/626993-louvre-heist-was-inside-job/'>RT</a>)</li><li>Lift manufacturer (reported reaction): The company that makes the basket lift used in the break-in has seen a surge of attention and media interest since the theft. (<a href='https://www.abc.net.au/news/2025-10-27/louvre-museum-heist-suspects-arrest-explainer/105937020'>ABC News Australia</a>)</li></ul><h3>Sources:</h3><ul><li><a href='https://abcnews.go.com/International/wireStory/timeline-jewel-heist-louvre-paris-126875373'>A timeline of the jewel heist at the Louvre in Paris</a> - abcnews.go.com</li><li><a href='https://www.theglobeandmail.com/world/video-suspects-arrested-in-louvre-jewel-heists-prosecutor-says/'>Suspects arrested in Louvre jewel heists, prosecutor says</a> - theglobeandmail.com</li><li><a href='https://www.npr.org/2025/10/27/nx-s1-5586619/suspects-arrested-in-brazen-louvre-museum-jewelry-heist'>Suspects arrested in brazen Louvre museum jewelry heist</a> - npr.org</li><li><a href='https://www.abc.net.au/news/2025-10-27/louvre-museum-heist-suspects-arrest-explainer/105937020'>Could the theft of gold and jewels from the Louvre have a silver lining?</a> - abc.net.au</li><li><a href='https://www.straitstimes.com/world/europe/louvre-heist-a-break-in-that-shook-france'>Louvre heist: A br